<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Access Denied — Montana MDT</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #1a1d2e; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .card {
    background: #1e2340; border: 1px solid #3a1a1a; border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 48px 40px; text-align: center; width: 400px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .icon { font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  h1 { color: #ff6b6b; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  p { color: #8890b0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  a { color: #5865F2; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="icon">🚫</div>
  <h1>Access Denied</h1>
  <p>You do not have the required department role to access the Montana MDT.<br><br>If you believe this is an error, contact your supervisor.</p>
  <a href="/login">← Back to Login</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
